{"lemma":"جُلَّةُ","slug":"جُلَّةُ","root":"ج.ل.ل","root_slug":"ج-ل-ل","root_link":"/words/roots/ج-ل-ل","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":false},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n6021","n6022","n6023","n6177","n6178"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AC%D9%8F%D9%84%D9%8E%D9%91%D8%A9%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":null,"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n6021","headword_ar":"جَلَّةٌ","root":"jl","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Mgh, Msb, K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jil~apN","text_ar":"جِلَّةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jul~apN","text_ar":"جُلَّةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) the second whereof is that which is most known [in the present day], and next the first [which seems to be the most chaste], (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Camels',"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sheep's,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"goats',"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"similar, dung;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baEarN","text_ar":"بَعَرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a single lump thereof:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, Msb, K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"such as has not been broken."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) [Commonly applied in the present day to"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such dung kneaded with chopped straw and formed into round flat cakes, which are dried in the sun, for fuel."},{"kind":"text","text":"] You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_in~a baniY fulaAnK wa quwduhumu Aljal~apu","text_ar":"اـِنَّ بَنِى فُلَانٍ وَ قُودُهُمُ الجَلَّةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Verily the sons of such a one, their fuel is the dung of camels"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sheep"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.]. (S.) ―         -b2-  Also (metonymically, Mgh) applied to"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Human ordure."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, Msb.)"}],"source_refs":["S","Mgh","Msb","K","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n6022","headword_ar":"جُلَّةٌ","root":"jl","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A large"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"receptacle made of palm-leaves woven together, such as is called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"quf~ap","text_ar":"قُفَّة"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"for dates;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a receptacle"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Mgh, Msb, K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"for dates,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Mgh, Msb,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"made of palm-leaves;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K;) ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a thing made of palm-leaves woven together, generally used as a receptacle for dates, but also employed for other purposes, as, for instance, to lay upon the mouth of a watering-trough, where the water is poured in, by way of protection;"},{"kind":"text","text":"see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_izaA='N","text_ar":"اـِزَا=ءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":":] pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jilaAlN","text_ar":"جِلَالٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, Msb, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"julalN","text_ar":"جُلَلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.)       -A2-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jal~ahN","text_ar":"جَلَّهٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":["S","Mgh","Msb","K"]},{"entry_id":"n6023","headword_ar":"جِلَّةٌ","root":"jl","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jal~apN","text_ar":"جَلَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":":       -A2-  and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaliylN","text_ar":"جَلِيلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; of which it is in most instances a pl."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n6177","headword_ar":"جَلِهَ","root":"jlh","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Msb, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jalahN","text_ar":"جَلَهٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Sudot;, * Msb, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, bald in the fore part of the head:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the greater part of his head."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.) [The latter seems to be the correct meaning: see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jalahN","text_ar":"جَلَهٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"below.] ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jalihato saAHatuhu","text_ar":"جَلِهَتْ سَاحَتُهُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"His court,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"yard, was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, vacant,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"void."},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jalaha","text_ar":"جَلَهَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jalohN","text_ar":"جَلْهٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He uncovered"},{"kind":"text","text":"a thing; or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"removed"},{"kind":"text","text":"it [from a thing that it covered or concealed]. (K, TA.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He raised"},{"kind":"text","text":"the turban,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"while folding it, from the side of his forehead"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eano jabiynihi","text_ar":"عَنْ جَبِينِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"), (K, TA,) [like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AijotalaY","text_ar":"اِجْتَلَى"},{"kind":"text","text":",]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and from the fore part of his head."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He removed"},{"kind":"text","text":"the pebbles from a place. (S, K.) ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He turned back"},{"kind":"text","text":"a person"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from a difficult,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hard, thing"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"affair."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.)"}],"source_refs":["S","Msb","K","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n6178","headword_ar":"جَلَهٌ","root":"jlh","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (JK, S,) or ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jalohapN","text_ar":"جَلْهَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Baldness in the fore part of the head;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"which is the beginning of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SalaEN","text_ar":"صَلَعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":";"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jalaHN","text_ar":"جَلَحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"baldness of the greater part of the head;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"more than"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jalaHN","text_ar":"جَلَحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (JK,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and more than"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SalaEN","text_ar":"صَلَعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", which is more than"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jalaHN","text_ar":"جَلَحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Msb in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jlH","text_ar":"جلح"},{"kind":"text","text":".)"}],"source_refs":["JK","S","K"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}